      • CursorAdapter

        public static final int[] CursorAdapter
        Adapter used to bind cursors.

        Includes the following attributes:

        AttributeDescription
        com.hero.rssreader:layout Layout resource used to display each row from the cursor.
        com.hero.rssreader:selection Selection statement for the query.
        com.hero.rssreader:sortOrder Sort order statement for the query.
        com.hero.rssreader:uri URI to get the cursor from.
        另请参阅:
        CursorAdapter_layout, CursorAdapter_selection, CursorAdapter_sortOrder, CursorAdapter_uri
